race.comment: Lots of these look close to getting off the mark. REGAL GENT (2) has raced four times and keeps improving, the latest a fast finishing second when having first try over the mile. Looks overdue and will be tough to stop again. HALF SCOTCH (6) has been thereabouts over 1400m the last couple, placing most recently. First try the trip and should be at top now. KAMAROOKA (7) is better than recent form suggests and gets chance to atone. CATALONA (3) is heading in the right direction having improved at each of three starts. Last start finished 1.3 lengths away in second over 1600m at Hamilton. Expected to run well again.
